Name: autoimmune pancreatitis
Definition: An autoimmune disease of endocrine system that is located_in the pancreas.

Name: pancreatic agenesis
Definition: A pancreas disease that is characterized by the failure of the pancreas to develop prior to birth.

Name: obsolete CLONE OF congenital afibrinogenemia
Definition: A pancreas disease that is characterized by the failure of the pancreas to develop prior to birth.

Name: annular pancreas
Definition: A pancreas disease characterized by autosomal dominant inheritance of the annular pancreas (head of the pancreas forming a ring around the second portion of the duodenum) and duodenal stenosis.

Name: pancreatic steatorrhea
Definition: A bone remodeling disease that has_material_basis_in impaired mineralization or calcification of bones before epiphyseal closure due to deficiency or impaired metabolism of vitamin D

Name: neurohypophyseal diabetes insipidus
Definition: An impaired renal function disease characterized by a complete or partial resistance of the kidneys to vasopressin (ADH).

Name: obsolete acute erythremia and erythroleukemia
Definition: An impaired renal function disease characterized by a complete or partial resistance of the kidneys to vasopressin (ADH).

Name: obsolete leukemic reticuloendotheliosis involving lymph nodes of head
Definition: An impaired renal function disease characterized by a complete or partial resistance of the kidneys to vasopressin (ADH).
Synonym: Leukemic reticuloendotheliosis of lymph nodes of head

Name: pancreatic mucinous ductal ectasia
Definition: A peritonitis which involves inflammation of peritoneal cavity by Corynebacterium diphtheriae.

Name: obsolete relapsing pancreatitis
Definition: A peritonitis which involves inflammation of peritoneal cavity by Corynebacterium diphtheriae.

Name: exocrine pancreatic insufficiency
Definition: A peritonitis which involves inflammation of peritoneal cavity by Corynebacterium diphtheriae.

Name: endocrine pancreas disease
Definition: A vulvar disease that is characterized by the presence of atrophy and associated with decreased estrogenization.

Name: pancreatic cancer
Definition: An endocrine gland cancer located_in the pancreas.

Name: pancreatic cystadenoma
Definition: A lung cancer that derives_from epithelial cells of glandular origin.

Name: pancreatitis
Definition: A poliomyelitis that results in destruction located in motor neurons
